## [ok]  1 constructor/1 (postprocessor)
## [ok]  2 enter/1..3    (string ?from to?)
## [ok]  3 read/1..3     (channel ?from to?)
## [ok]  4 enter-more/1  (string)
## [ok]  5 read-more/1   (chan)
## [ok]  6 location/0    ()
## [ok]  7 stop/0        ()
## [ok]  8 dont-stop/0   ()
## [ok]  9 from/1..      (pos ...)
## [ok] 10 relative/1    (delta)
## [ok] 11 rewind/1      (delta)
## [ok] 12 to/1          (pos)
